    "description": "A virus rewires the frayed roots of the forest, overwriting flora, glitching fauna, and changing the code of nature itself. Forest's mage Anaiah enlists the help of paladin Finn to hack the corruption rotting the Core. The pair must learn to work together, harvest The Additive, and reboot the Core to its natural state.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as Two Fight as One</strong></h2>Explore Anaiah and Finn's dynamic as you switch between a mid-ranged mage and a close-combat paladin.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/c87c0d57c63ae3b507e8c133f127362e.poster.avif?t=1666843220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/c87c0d57c63ae3b507e8c133f127362e.webm?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/c87c0d57c63ae3b507e8c133f127362e.mp4?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Never Fight Alone</strong></h2>Though things feel bleak, there's still someone ready to fight by your side!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/ac0610b8b1a09071472d17f912978f2b.poster.avif?t=1666843220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/ac0610b8b1a09071472d17f912978f2b.webm?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/ac0610b8b1a09071472d17f912978f2b.mp4?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Navigate Nature's Obstacles</strong></h2>Slash through twisted roots and restore energy to flowers as you work through the forest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/5747384ea3601341d1eef48c944b0a85.poster.avif?t=1666843220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/5747384ea3601341d1eef48c944b0a85.webm?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/5747384ea3601341d1eef48c944b0a85.mp4?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the Elements</strong></h2>Harness the elements of Control, Stability, and Power as you search for The Additive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/6fb6fdab84090914e0b569986938ac61.poster.avif?t=1666843220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/6fb6fdab84090914e0b569986938ac61.webm?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/6fb6fdab84090914e0b569986938ac61.mp4?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover a Pixilated Digital Forest</h2>Venture through a unique and detailed world of nature and neon in this techno-nature world. Here, technology is nature, with energy running through the roots of the forest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/597d3d1a87e2f8adba563c753787a589.poster.avif?t=1666843220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/597d3d1a87e2f8adba563c753787a589.webm?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184460/extras/597d3d1a87e2f8adba563c753787a589.mp4?t=1666843220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pre Alpha Demo Notes</strong></h2>Our demo is in a pre-alpha state, meaning this is just a slice of our intended vision, and there are lil bugs squirming around our dear code. UpRooted is in active development, so we fully plan to squash those pests! Along with bug fixing, our future focuses will be wired towards polishing our buddy and enemy AI, adding save systems, dialogue systems, new levels, creatures, powers, puzzles, and more! This demo is only the start of the story we want to tell. So stay tuned for more!",
